<div class="static_content">
	<h2>The edu<font color="#e81657">OER</font> front-end portal</h2>
	<p class="intro">
		Open educational resources (OER) are rapidly becoming a major factor
		for education at all levels. During the last years, the OER community
		has grown considerably and the impact of OER on educational systems
		has become an issue of public policy. In this context, the GEANT
		community decided to create the edu<font color="#e81657">OER</font> portal, in order to help
		students, educators, and content creators find content across diverse
		resources, disc​iplines and countries. <br> <br> The edu<font color="#e81657">OER</font> portal
		provides users with the means to search and find open educational
		multimedia content across multiple disciplines, countries and
		languages in order to re-use, revise, remix or redistribute it. The
		content is divided by repository catalog (coming from various
		Universities, NRENs, European organizations etc.) and by subject.
	</p>
